  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442350/extras/262760503dfa674a2395833b6c7612c5.avif?t=1609956481\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><br>Become the legendary Warior in the Space. Play single-player across large exotic maps. Think tactical, be quick against the time and enjoy the adventure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2><br>After World War 3, the earth is no more livible. Richest people escape to the Space and make their own habitat. Other imprisoned in the world. That's why a girl named Bettie create a 5 person team and start a riot.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>3 Levels to complete</li><li>Vibrant animations</li><li>Exotic futuristic maps </li><li>Hard levels</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442350/extras/da713b3cecb67f60318a150a8b95da41.avif?t=1609956481\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442350/extras/cef0b36a35103244ae99de3d4b18f147.avif?t=1609956481\" width=600 height=307 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442350/extras/753864981b09c0e3121f0c9e06f07c1e.avif?t=1609956481\" width=600 height=246 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442350/extras/40104b2ee7c931b9e06e0d00f1ef94ae.avif?t=1609956481\" width=250 height=414 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1442350/extras/c9b6b0c7d23cea3708923c3fa315749c.avif?t=1609956481\" widt